0.3 04dec2025
* added norwegian translation, thanks to user Aslak
* additional documentation
* error handling in installer
* handle if current working directory is not available
* fix error caused by missing pressure
* check for the existence of the extension's `lang` directory
* added slovak translation, thanks to user Tomáš
* replace `merge_config` by `conditional_merge` to preserve existing keys
* new option `disable_pyephem` to disable the default almanac
* handle unknown Earth satellites
* `weectl` option `--download-ephemeris` to download ephemerides during installation
* `weectl` option `--skip-localization` for user Michael K.
